00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:20,180
 past two months.

201
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:21,620
 It's in Acts 2.

202
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:27,060
 They devoted themselves to the apostles' teaching and to fellowship and to the breaking of bread

203
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:28,820
 and to prayer.

204
00:20:28,820 --> 00:20:34,420
 Everyone was filled with awe at the many wonders and signs performed by the apostles.

205
00:20:34,420 --> 00:20:38,900
 All the believers were together and had everything in common.

206
00:20:38,900 --> 00:20:43,660
 They sold property and possessions to give to anyone who had need.

207
00:20:43,660 --> 00:20:47,140
 Every day, they continued to meet together in the temple courts.

208
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:48,740
 They broke bread in their homes.

209
00:20:48,740 --> 00:20:54,780
 They ate together with glad and sincere hearts, praising God and enjoying the favor of all

