00:31:23,900 --> 00:31:26,860
 me in your prayers.

325
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:34,820
 I have terminal cancer and I have been told I haven't much time left.

326
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:40,660
 A prayer for me would be such a comfort.

327
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:42,900
 Bless you."

